scenes.description: Opening splash screen for hololive 5th fes. Capture the Moment stage 3, featuring the main visual and hashtags.
Notice screen for visitors regarding venue rules, including lighting effects and cheering guidelines.
Display of official event merchandise such as T-shirts, towels, and penlights.
Sales information detailing the schedules for on-site sales and post-event mail order.
Montage section showing a continuous scroll of messages from fans and hololive members.
